Product description

Designed to give ultimate comfort, this school bag from Cosmus is a Multipurpose Backpack Bag use it as school bag or regular casual backpack for daily use.  This school bag is designed with copious space and sturdy shoulder straps to help children accommodate all essentials while on the move. Key Features High on quality and durability Attractive design Spacious to accommodate all essentials Two main compartment, two front compartment Two side Mesh pockets Specifications Material PU coated Polyester Fabric. Dimensions: 13 x 18 x 8.5 [inches] (WxHxD); Weight: 755 gms Suggestive Age - 8 Years+

Product Description

Cosmus Madison 2 compartments Large Navy Blue / Black /Grey/Royal Blue Laptop backpack

Perfect for daily commuter or occasional traveller, this strong backpack is loaded with pockets/compartments to hold all your important documents.15.6 inches premium Laptop backpack is made from High-Grade polyester fabric and features a well organized design with high quality fittings.

Some silent features are -

1 :- Laptop compartment

2 :- Capacity of 33L and can easily carry weight

3 :- 2 big compartments and 2 external Front pockets.

4 :- Two sided pockets & water bottle holder

5 :- Waterproof & long lasting.

Padded straps

This travel laptop backpack suits your style to look modern and fashionable & is very comfortable to carry. Thick and well padded shoulder straps makes the bag feel lighter while carrying. Breathable and adjustable shoulder straps relieve the stress on your shoulders and gives your back comfort and very a good support. A well furnished and sturdy top handle ensures comfort for long hours carrying.

Cushioned and Adjustable Straps

The bag has been designed with cushioned shoulder straps that do not cause discomfort when carrying the bag for long. Besides, the straps are also adjustable to provide each individual with the comfort they need.

Laptop compartment

Satellite Laptop backpack is a perfect Laptop bag for daily use, its cushioned pocket keeps your Laptop secure,Compatible for 15.6 inches

Lock Type

Butterfly lock is the lock type for this backpack. This lock provides enhanced security.

his backpack consists of 2 compartments. Therefore, you can carry all your essentials without any worries.

This backpack comes with versatile usage facility. This backpack can also be used for carrying papers, documents, bottles, etc.

How are ratings calculated?
To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we don’t use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyses reviews to verify trustworthiness.
